						<h3 class="md:ml-auto md:text-xl max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-75">Design and technology make a great pairing‚Äîluckily, I have a background in both. Currently, I'm a VP of Product Design at a Brooklyn-based startup.</h3>
