								body="<ul class='list-disc pl-5'><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Won two Communicator Awards: the Award of Excellence in Food & Beverage for PotatoesUSA and the Award of Visual Appeal for Fossil Trace Golf Club, both highlighting my ability to develop creative and effective web designs.</li><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Used user-centered design techniques and current best practices to design and build each client's website, providing high-quality, impact-driven web solutions.</li><li class='mb-0 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Delivered new websites every week while meeting aggressive timelines and maintaining high quality.</li></ul>"
